Package: echosmart-gateway
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9),
         python3-requests,
         python3-dotenv,
         python3-paho-mqtt,
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: mosquitto-clients, sqlite3
Suggests: python3-rpi.gpio, python3-smbus
Description: EchoSmart IoT Gateway for precision agriculture
 Sensor hub that runs on Raspberry Pi to collect environmental
 data (temperature, humidity, light, soil moisture, CO₂) and
 relay it to the EchoSmart cloud platform via MQTT.
 .
 Includes five sensor drivers (DS18B20, DHT22, BH1750,
 SoilMoisture+ADS1115, MH-Z19C), local SQLite caching, alert
 engine, and automatic cloud synchronisation.
